          <summary>How long will it be until I get my hands on a Wayki of my own?</summary>
          <p>Broadly speaking, we already have a physical prototype and have identified the factories we'll be using in China. We're also preparing the PCB for production but the main time consuming process lies with getting the professional moulds developed. We're estimating 3 - 5 months for batch 1 (determined by number of pre-orders) but make sure you get onto our newsletter to stay up to date at http://www.wayki.co. I'll be checkpointing every step of the way on the blog, and we welcome you to leave comments. You can even share your morning horror stories if the urge takes you!</p></details>
      </li>
