          <summary>What will I do about replacement brushes?</summary>
          <p>Our brushes will be available via the main website (<a href="http://wayki.co" target="_blank">Wayki.co</a>) soon after Wayki has been ratcheted up to mass production. That's all we can reveal at this point but we can say the following:
<br>- Affordable price point, competing with the cost of existing electric toothbrush heads
<br>- New designs will be introduced as time goes on plus added personalisation options will be considered if there is demand.
